te <strong>Stan W Decker</strong> <a href=\"mailto:stanwdecker@gmail.com\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-187 size-full\" src=\"https://awards.france-metal.fr/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Mail-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"23\" height=\"15\" /></a> <a class=\"btn black\" href=\"http://www.stanwdartworks.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Site web  </a><strong>Sicca</strong> <a href=\"mailto:laurent.juy@gmail.com\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-187 size-full\" src=\"https://awards.france-metal.fr/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Mail-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"23\" height=\"15\" /></a><a class=\"btn black\" href=\"http://sicca-area.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"> Site web\n</a>Photographes <strong>Kermhit</strong> (Centre) <a class=\"btn black\" href=\"mailto:kermhit.asso@hotmail.fr\">Mail</a>', 'Qui sommes nous ?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-05 17:53:57', '2018-01-05 16:53:57', '', 50, 'https://awards.france-metal.fr/2017/12/19/50-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
